{
  "stem": "10549.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was much better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had guards over us and yelling at us and watching us over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but there was still much better conditions than going to-- every morning to the woods and digging the stumps out of the frozen ground, at that-- at that-- that cold weather too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's what I was at the-- at that-- at that factory, until-- until April.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And gets to spring was a little better.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in spring-- I mean in April [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 8-- no, April 10-- April 10-- there was a few days before my birthday.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They loaded us on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they never tell us where we're going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And each time they just tell us that we, just like cattle, listen to what they-- what they-- what we have to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we followed them because all that was us-- guards with guns and things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we listened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They loaded us on the trucks, open trucks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were on the road for maybe three, four hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all of sudden the trucks stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the guards disappeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And before we know, there was American tanks came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And naturally, the first reaction was, we jumped off the trucks, and we felt that we are free.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The American troops are here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In those trucks--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--might have been maybe around 200.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like three, four trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we-- we were beside ourselves, you know, that all of the sudden, the guards disappeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we feel that we are free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first thing, we were starving.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
